This is a normal citizen.
You must clean the trash, or else the citizen would not care about the environment anymore and will throw more trash
Use "C" to clean the trash, when near the trash
Use "X" key to catch the bad guys who polluting the environment
When the citizen became more corrupted, they will turn to a bad guy. Catch them to re-educate them on being a good environmentalist.
Tips: You can get more handcuffs by cleaning the trash.
Clean up the trash, and catch all the polluter to go to the next stage!
